{"tid":2081133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：行普通法的加拿大 必須尊重中國法治精神","createTime":"2020-06-27T03:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T04:36:36.000Z","uid":7542,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"923741b3db445317ef2262cc335490104a032b09","tid":2081133,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>每次聽到某國批評人哋嘅司法觀念<br />\n就好似一個窮人批評李嘉誠唔識投資</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國駐加拿大大使館對加方，就兩名在中國被拘押的加拿大公民案件的言論，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，再次敦促加方認真對待中方嚴正立場，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>切實尊重法治精神和中國司法主權</strong></span>，停止發表不負責任的言論，停止通過搞<span style=\"color: red;\">「麥克風外交」</span>對華施壓。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中方表示，中國司法機關依法獨立辦案</strong></span>，兩名加國公民康明凱及邁克爾的犯罪事實清楚，證據確實、充分，根本不存在所謂「任意拘押」情況，又指中國電訊設備商華為副董事長孟晚舟事件，是美國為了打壓中國高科技企業和華為，而策劃的一起嚴重政治事件，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">批評加方充當美方幫兇，這才是「任意拘押」，呼籲加方停止政治操弄</span></strong>，立即釋放孟晚舟。加拿大總理杜魯多早前表示，不會透過釋放孟晚舟，換取康明凱及邁克爾獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534395-20200627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534395-20200627.htm&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=4d52ae58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534395-20200627.htm&h=afe8ec1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534395-20200627.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=be5f89de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>剪片時聽了超過十次，但每次都起哂雞皮，去到最後都係忍唔住喊。<br />\n<br />\n如果你開始恐懼、退縮、氣餒 &mdash; 閉起雙眼，由頭聽到尾。提醒自己，你不是孤單的；亦不要讓其他抗爭者感到孤單。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4eab6454a0271f92cbea50151f7de232c0dae989","tid":2081133,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"打佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dcccf8eb00a1134609303c7ae558801362f6ce","tid":2081133,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"美加公開聆訊 所有證據擺晒出嚟<br />\n被告有得請律師 有充分機會抗辯<br />\n支那呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81539eef815f7a22cba2a72d4ff1eb73ccfaa9","tid":2081133,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"自己向人施壓好話人向佢施壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7181a043981a2dfc9faabf89446dfc18b1e5d502","tid":2081133,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"太監教人扑嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c29390f6deef9f271379b8ffa43a549bcd1d15f","tid":2081133,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"4bc67941fe3a6fb4be867a3d5c4c6bc70221f1ab","tid":2081133,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:50:19.000Z","msg":"即係話， 受害者西方各國必須尊重罪犯支那，不要反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373bf338e5238d2f84141deeec0fe7e1ac5d7785","tid":2081133,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"中國法治係大笑話"},{"pid":"d7be2ca2baae5658ec97eb22cdccad29b9b48152","tid":2081133,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"最好死刑兩個加拿大人<br />\n加速加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39918149b182e107427745c2208ec00472ae8ce0","tid":2081133,"uid":498,"l